{"tid":1580200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"俄演員無故被控襲警 普京：影片不能成為證據","createTime":"2019-09-19T03:03:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T03:13:48.000Z","uid":200758,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bb5f47a4fe939c9331cbf5fa5d120a8b83b57044","tid":1580200,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T03:03:08.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯民眾示威聲援被指襲擊警察判監 3 年半的演員。 <br />\n<br />\n約 100 人在莫斯科集會包括多位著名演員，他們輪流在總統府門外展示海報聲援烏斯季諾夫。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在 7 月底的反政府示威中，多名防暴警察被拍到突然拘捕正在看手機的烏斯季諾夫，並揮動警棍。烏斯季諾夫其後被控襲警，法官在庭上拒絕辯方要求翻查影片，判他監禁 3 年半。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總統普京發言人表示這段影片不能成為任何法律行為的基礎，只可等待上訴結果。"},{"pid":"7bc77c43b5d0aa3d14b09a1b370fb8915c031680","tid":1580200,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T03:03:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/557490/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E4%BF%84%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E6%BC%94%E5%93%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F557490%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E4%25BF%2584%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%258F%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%2594%25E5%2593%25A1&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5cwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=6d622809\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F557490%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E4%25BF%2584%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%258F%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%2594%25E5%2593%25A1&h=74407a60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/557490/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E4%BF%84%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E7%A4%B